<pc>，</pc>耶律宗福安國軍<term>節度使</term>
<pc>。</pc>冬<measure quantity="10" unit="months">
<num value="10">十</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>駐蹕遼河<pc>。</pc>宋遣蔡齊<pc>、</pc>李用和來賀<num value="1000">千</num>齡節<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="11" unit="months">
<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>追封南院大王韓制心為陳王<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
<num value="12">十二</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>以蕭從政為歸義軍<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>康筠監門衛<pc>，</pc>充賀宋正旦使副<pc>。</pc>是年<pc>，</pc>放進士李訁恣等<measure quantity="47" unit="people">
